<figureCitation box="[1261,1334,513,536]" captionStart="FIGURES 47–52" captionStartId="15.[151,264,1887,1911]" captionTargetBox="[166,1423,188,1854]" captionTargetId="figure-15@15.[151,1436,181,1863]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURES 47–52. Lethierium grandilobum sp. nov., holotype, male genitalia. 47—anal tube, pygofer, and penis, lateral view; 48—anal tube, dorsal view; 49—penis and connective, lateral view; 50—penis and connective, ventral view; 51—style, lateral view; 52—style, dorsal view. Out of scale." pageId="2" pageNumber="519">Fig. 47</figureCitation>
). Lobes of phallobase basement enlarged apically (
<figureCitation box="[608,680,543,565]" captionStart="FIGURES 47–52" captionStartId="15.[151,264,1887,1911]" captionTargetBox="[166,1423,188,1854]" captionTargetId="figure-15@15.[151,1436,181,1863]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURES 47–52. Lethierium grandilobum sp. nov., holotype, male genitalia. 47—anal tube, pygofer, and penis, lateral view; 48—anal tube, dorsal view; 49—penis and connective, lateral view; 50—penis and connective, ventral view; 51—style, lateral view; 52—style, dorsal view. Out of scale." pageId="2" pageNumber="519">Fig. 49</figureCitation>
). Style with weakly concave hind margin (
<figureCitation box="[1091,1162,543,565]" captionStart="FIGURES 47–52" captionStartId="15.[151,264,1887,1911]" captionTargetBox="[166,1423,188,1854]" captionTargetId="figure-15@15.[151,1436,181,1863]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURES 47–52. Lethierium grandilobum sp. nov., holotype, male genitalia. 47—anal tube, pygofer, and penis, lateral view; 48—anal tube, dorsal view; 49—penis and connective, lateral view; 50—penis and connective, ventral view; 51—style, lateral view; 52—style, dorsal view. Out of scale." pageId="2" pageNumber="519">Fig. 51</figureCitation>
). 
<collectingCountry box="[1179,1266,543,564]" name="Morocco" pageId="2" pageNumber="519">Morocco</collectingCountry>
............................................................................................... 
