<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,220,682]" pageId="2" pageNumber="519">
<keyLead pageId="2" pageNumber="519">
- Metope with weakly concave upper margin (
<figureCitation box="[650,723,601,623]" captionStart="FIGURES 9–11" captionStartId="6.[151,264,1757,1781]" captionTargetBox="[170,1420,788,1682]" captionTargetId="figure-298@6.[151,1436,776,1701]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURES 9–11. Lethierium cedricolum (Dlabola, 1989), male, Timhadit. 9—dorsal view; 10—lateral view; 11—frontal view. Scale bar—1 mm." pageId="2" pageNumber="519">Figs 11</figureCitation>
