<figureCitation box="[1128,1200,631,653]" captionStart="FIGURES 41–46" captionStartId="14.[151,264,1513,1537]" captionTargetBox="[158,1430,188,1454]" captionTargetId="figure-28@14.[151,1436,181,1462]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURES 41–46. Lethierium cedricolum (Dlabola, 1989), Timhadit, male genitalia. 41—anal tube and pygofer, lateral view; 42—anal tube, dorsal view; 43—style, lateral view; 44—style, dorsal view; 45—penis, ventral view; 46—penis and connective, lateral view. Out of scale." pageId="2" pageNumber="519">Fig. 43</figureCitation>
